Audio Formats: ''Ramona Quimby, Age 8'' is available in cassette, CD and eAudiobook from Random House/Listening Library; VHs tape from Atlantis Films/Ramona Productions;<ref name=Editions>{{cite web | title = Formats and Editions | work = Ramona Quimby, Age 8 | url =http://www.worldcat.org/title/ramona-quimby-age-8/oclc/7639046/editions?referer=di&editionsView=true&fq= |accessdate = April 29, 2012 }}</ref>

