Print/Worldwide: As of 2010, 137 editions of ''Ramona Quimby, Age 8'' had been published in 8 languages.<ref>{{cite web | title = Editions | work = Beverly Cleary | http://worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n50-40968| accessdate = April 29, 2012 }}</ref>

